      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been absolutely babied and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a scratch or smudge anywhere! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
